WEBVTT

00:01.036 --> 00:02.097
Giving Directions

00:03.360 --> 00:06.851
Excuse me, how do I get to the Convention Center?

00:13.559 --> 00:16.440
It's easy. Keep driving straight ahead.

00:22.643 --> 00:24.860
Keep going straight across the bridge.

00:30.859 --> 00:32.135
Turn left on Park Road.

00:38.249 --> 00:40.549
It's the first exit after you get off the bridge.

00:46.394 --> 00:47.889
Turn right before the factory.

00:53.901 --> 00:55.565
Go through the next intersection.

01:01.594 --> 01:03.397
Go past the big building.

01:09.476 --> 01:11.599
Take your next left and park.

01:17.543 --> 01:19.215
Get out and cross the street.

01:25.131 --> 01:26.365
Walk through the park.

01:32.360 --> 01:36.460
You are there. You can't miss it. It's a huge building.

01:42.474 --> 01:44.030
Thanks! You've been a big help.

